import { Typography, FormControl, InputLabel, InputAdornment, Input, TextField } from "@mui/material"
import { Box } from "@mui/system"
import Log from '../assets/background/back.svg'

const Login = () => {

    return(
        <Box>
            <Box component='img' src={Log} position='absolute'/>
            <Box position='relative'>
                <Box sx={{
                    position: 'absolute',
                    top: '50%',
                    left: '50%',
                    background: 'white'
                }}>
                    <Typography>Sign In</Typography>
                    <Typography width='65%'>Please sign up to your personal account if you want to use all our premium products</Typography>
                    <FormControl variant="standard">
                    <InputLabel htmlFor="input-with-icon-adornment">
                    With a start adornment
                    </InputLabel>
                    <TextField
                    variant="outlined"
                    id="input-with-icon-adornment"
                    startAdornment={
                        <InputAdornment position="start">
                        </InputAdornment>
                    }
                    />
                </FormControl>
                </Box>
            </Box>
        </Box>
    )
}

export default Login
